06:37.738 --> 06:39.729
Yeah, yeah, yeah. Hop in my truck.

06:41.810 --> 06:43.745
- Good night.
- I got room. Who needs a ride?

06:44.413 --> 06:47.143
Hey, guys, let's go.
We gotta go before the cops come.

06:49.018 --> 06:50.714
Sarah wants you, man.

06:50.888 --> 06:53.551
- That's bullshit.
- Oh, now. Don't be jealous, Reid.

06:55.527 --> 06:57.996
- My car won't start!
