14:45.116 --> 14:46.481
So we are interested.

14:50.523 --> 14:52.990
- So who's the fifth?
- Fifth what?

14:53.158 --> 14:55.424
Well, you said five families.

14:55.795 --> 14:58.129
They say the fifth was killed
during the witch-hunt.

14:58.298 --> 15:00.961
- What?
- Cool, huh?

15:01.336 --> 15:03.133
Or creepy.

15:10.847 --> 15:13.410
Couldn't see nothing but their taillights
in the damn fog.

15:13.585 --> 15:14.745
But I swear to God...

15:14.920 --> 15:17.753
...it sure seemed like
they went right off the damn cliffs.

15:20.093 --> 15:21.721
What you were
probably looking at...

15:21.896 --> 15:25.354
...were the aircraft warning lights
on the Marblehead lighthouse.

15:25.534 --> 15:28.971
<i>Captain, we have a suspect vehicle
with occupant back near the Dells.</i>

15:29.138 --> 15:31.232
<i>Respond and advise.</i>

15:45.292 --> 15:47.853
We tried to wake him,
but he's passed out cold.

15:48.028 --> 15:49.155
