16:15.429 --> 16:16.897
Son.

17:04.256 --> 17:05.917
Somebody there?

17:23.515 --> 17:25.211
Hello?

17:34.161 --> 17:35.890
Hello?

19:27.037 --> 19:29.198
- Oh, my God.
- Didn't mean to scare you.

19:29.372 --> 19:30.963
- Oh, my God.
- Just got back.

19:31.742 --> 19:34.506
Sorry. I'm just a little freaked out.

19:34.679 --> 19:36.978
