21:10.098 --> 21:11.259
<i>Caleb?</i>

21:27.687 --> 21:29.587
<i>What's going on, Caleb? Pick up.</i>

21:29.757 --> 21:32.486
<i>Caleb, pick up the phone, man.</i>

21:33.027 --> 21:34.496
Caleb, what's going on?

21:35.497 --> 21:37.830
I just saw a darkling.

21:38.001 --> 21:40.662
It was in the form of that dead kid
they found at the Dells.

21:40.837 --> 21:42.965
I saw his picture this morning
in the newspaper.

21:43.140 --> 21:46.132
<i>- But who'd send you a darkling?
- I have no idea.</i>

21:46.311 --> 21:48.371
<i>Something's wrong. I can feel it.</i>

21:48.548 --> 21:50.105
We gotta talk to Reid tonight.

21:50.283 --> 21:51.580
<i>He'll probably be at Nicky's.</i>

21:51.751 --> 21:53.219
<i>- We'll see him then.
- Definitely.</i>

22:19.552 --> 22:21.214
- Here you go, Caleb.
- Thanks.

22:21.387 --> 22:23.015
Hey, Caleb.

22:23.189 --> 22:26.592
- Oh, hey, Kate. What are you up to?
- I'm just stocking up our room.

22:27.262 --> 22:30.756
- Did you hear about the dead kid?
- Yeah, I did.

22:31.468 --> 22:32.729
Did you know him?

22:33.469 --> 22:36.235
