22:36.407 --> 22:38.603
Yeah, I heard he lived on
Reid and Tyler's floor.

22:40.645 --> 22:43.012
- Hi.
- Hi there.

22:46.185 --> 22:47.847
You scared me.

22:48.021 --> 22:49.923
- Hey, man.
- Hey.

22:50.258 --> 22:53.853
I'm gonna see if Pogue wants to catch
that new Brad Pitt flick this afternoon.

22:54.028 --> 22:56.293
- Who else wants to go?
- I will.

22:57.066 --> 22:59.728
I gotta run some errands
for my mother.

22:59.969 --> 23:01.061
I already saw it.

23:02.771 --> 23:05.298
- Do you feel like running errands?
- Sure.

23:29.039 --> 23:32.339
I wish I'd brought my camera.
This place is so beautiful.

23:39.720 --> 23:42.712
That's the old Putnam barn.
What's left of it.

23:42.891 --> 23:46.019
