was the original Ipswich Colony.

23:50.800 --> 23:53.269
- So, what brought you to Spenser?
- A scholarship.

23:53.437 --> 23:56.338
- But why Spenser?
- I want to go to Harvard.

23:56.506 --> 23:59.636
- My father was class of '81.
- That's so cool.

24:01.513 --> 24:05.474
- Kate told me he passed away.
- You and Kate talk about me?

24:06.287 --> 24:08.846
Well, you know, just girl stuff.

24:34.221 --> 24:36.954
It's our family's first colony house.

24:39.127 --> 24:43.657
- Wait. Somebody lives here?
- Just our caretaker, Gorman.

24:45.669 --> 24:47.568
Gorman! It's me! It's okay!

24:48.037 --> 24:50.506
- He doesn't see that well anymore.
- You think?

24:51.543 --> 24:54.911
- Who's with you?
- Just a friend.

24:55.080 --> 24:57.744
- I'll be right back, okay?
- Okay.

25:33.128 --> 25:34.857
Caleb.

25:37.934 --> 25:41.099
- You should be more careful.
- I know, Gorman.

25:43.340 --> 25:46.505
- Is there anything else he needs?
- No.

25:47.746 --> 25:49.737
I'll see you next week, then.

26:07.137 --> 26:10.472
- Okay?
- Yeah. Yeah, I'm okay.

26:11.010 --> 26:13.444
So you wanna shower
or change first?

26:13.613 --> 26:17.016
