27:16.091 --> 27:18.615
- Corner pocket.
- Great shot.

27:24.000 --> 27:26.629
Well, well, well...

27:26.806 --> 27:28.797
- How long you guys been here?
- A bit.

27:28.973 --> 27:33.570
